Download Spark

rename tgz file to spark.tgz

in the home directory

mkdir spark

cd spark

tar -xvzf ~/Downloads/spark.tgz --strip 1

cd ../

install 

pip3 install findspark

cd spark

then type pwd to get directory. copy it.

/home/camagakhan/spark

to add pyspark

>>> import findspark
>>> findspark.init('/home/camagakhan/spark')
>>> import pyspark
